Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:40.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:96651,100113}{\i1}Mine Nozomi, born in poverty\Nto an owner of an oden stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:43.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:100113,103741}{\i1}After composer Egawa Isao\Nhad taken her in,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:103741,107370}{\i1}she began to work hard to one day\Nrealize her dream of becoming a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:54.37,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:108329,114377}{\i1}The one person that had supported her\Nthorough the struggle was a boxer called Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:59.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:115503,119841}{\i1}The time they spent together\Nhad been increasing day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:06.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:119841,126889}{\i1}But as they have realized that\Nit is a very important period for them:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:126889,129976}{\i1}music for Nozomi,\Nand boxing for Fanni,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:15.56,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:129976,135565}{\i1}they have decided to focus\Non their own paths for now.
