Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:34.16,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:151664,154167}The gong goes tonight!{NOTE:今夜決勝のゴング}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:153166,155543}{\i1}Rookie of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:155543,157587}{\i1}Fanni Moriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:40.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:157587,160131}{\i1}So that's Mine's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:161716,163301}I brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.30,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:163301,164302}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:53.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:168765,173186}Mine, I'm thinking seriously about\Nstarting evening classes with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:56.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:173186,176689}If you don't mind,\Nit'd be fabulous, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.94,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:176689,177940}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.56,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:177940,180568}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:180568,182111}How about we do it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.40,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:182111,184405}Yes. Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:08.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:184405,188242}If it suits you, sir,\NI'm more than okay to start today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.20,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:188242,190203}I see. Good. Today it is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:192663,194290}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:194290,195333}What is it, Sune?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.33,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:195333,197335}Ah, i-it's nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.37,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:198252,200379}Nozomi-chan,\Nare you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.80,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:202090,205802}Master wanted to be nice to you,\Nbut you weren't forced to say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:205802,207053}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.72,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:207053,208721}Then why did you\Nagree for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:209806,212767}If Fanny found out that I skipped\Nmy first lesson to cheer him on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:212767,215478}I don't think he'd be very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:39.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:215478,219148}Also, my goal is to be a singer.\NI've decided to do everything to reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:219148,221067}and not to pass any\Nopportunity to make progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.94,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:221067,222944}You'll become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:48.03,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:222944,228032}If I had your determination, maybe\NI could find a boyfriend like Fanni, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:228032,229450}Oh, come on, Sune-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.70,0:04:06.71,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:237708,246717}{\fad(3000,2000)\an8}All-Japan Professional Boxing\NFeatherweight Class{NOTE:全日本プロボクシング\\Nフェザー級\\N新人王決勝戦\\Nレフティー畑本対ファニー森山}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:06.71,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:237708,246717}{\fad(3000,2000)\an2}Rookie of the Year final match\NLefty Hatamoto vs. Fanni Moriyama{NOTE:全日本プロボクシング\\Nフェザー級\\N新人王決勝戦\\Nレフティー畑本対ファニー森山}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.55,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:249262,250555}{\i1}Watch me, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:12.76,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:250555,252765}{\i1}I'll do it. I know I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.18,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:257145,259188}Hello. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.10,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:259188,261107}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.52,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:261107,263526}Ah, I see. Please hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.65,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:263526,265653}Fanni. Some woman is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.15,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:265653,268156}So she's called, huh? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.65,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:268156,269657}Try to make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:32.03,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:269657,272034}We don't have much time.{NOTE:簡単に切り上げたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:35.49,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:272034,275496}Hello? I was just\Nthinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:275496,276914}I figured you'd call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:276914,278291}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:38.83,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:278291,278833}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.45,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:278833,280459}I see. I'm Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.83,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:280459,281836}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.75,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:281836,283754}Certainly not\Nthe person you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:49.38,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:284589,289385}But the girl you thought I'd be,\Nthe one that you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.97,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:289385,291971}do you have any idea\Nwho she really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:291971,294807}What are you talking about?\NWho the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.51,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:294807,296517}I think you'll know soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.02,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:299228,301022}Ah! Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.94,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:305526,306944}So it was a stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.57,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:306944,307570}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.40,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:307570,310406}It looked like she had something\Nto say to you, so I backed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.36,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:311616,314368}I dunno what it was,\Nbut don't let it get to you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.95,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:314368,316954}Stuff like that sometimes\Nhappens before matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.04,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:316954,319040}You've gotta focus\Non what's before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:319040,320041}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.04,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:323836,325046}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.29,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:325046,326297}Someone's here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.17,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:326297,328174}Huh? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:31.30,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:328174,331302}Do you even need to ask?\NAin't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:34.47,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:331302,334472}I'm sorry to disappoint you,\Nbut it's just your little brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.51,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:334472,336515}Huh? Little brother and sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.22,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:336515,338226}That's some mistake.\NI don't have—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.93,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:338226,339936}Hey, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:41.89,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:339936,341896}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.06,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:342521,344065}Ah, it's you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.77,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:344065,345775}You're Nozomi-chan's siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.81,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:345775,346817}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:52.82,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:348694,352823}Our big sis is studying with Mr. Composer,\Nso we're here instead of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.15,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:353658,355159}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:02.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:359247,362041}I can't believe\Nyou went that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.95,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:362041,362959}Thank you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.50,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:362959,365503}You must've traveled a long way\Nto get here. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.46,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:365503,368464}"Thank you"?\NDon't be such a cold fish, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.13,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:368464,370132}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.34,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:370132,371342}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:19.26,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:375012,379267}I mean, soon you'll be a real brother\Nto me and Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.55,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:379267,380559}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.56,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:380559,383562}You're gonna marry Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.98,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:383562,384981}Hey, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:29.94,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:384981,389944}She's right, you know. You're man\Nenough to get married soon, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.44,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:389944,391445}Coach…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:36.90,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:391445,396909}Hah, Fanni. You better win tonight's match,\Nor you'll lose face to your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.25,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:405293,407253}"To the eldest brother, Hisashi.\NGood luck."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.17,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:407253,409171}"From your little sister, Nozomi."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.67,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:410339,411674}Who did you get this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.88,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:412550,413884}Ah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.34,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:413884,416345}It was from some lady\Nnear the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.97,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:416345,419974}She said to give flowers\Nto our brother Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:02.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:419974,422310}Some lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.22,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:422310,424228}Yuki-chan, I have\Nto ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.18,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:424228,427189}What are your\Nmom and dad's names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:11.77,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:427189,431777}Dad is Shinsuke,\Nand Mom is Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:438993,441078}{\i1}Mine Shinsuke and Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.96,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:450254,451964}{\i1}Mine Shinsuke and Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.47,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:456844,458471}It's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.26,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:459430,461265}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.26,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:461265,463267}Let's go, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.68,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:465603,467688}{\i1}Mine Shinsuke and Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:467688,470316}{\i1}They're the same.\NThe names are completely the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:54.48,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:470316,474487}{\i1}They're the same as my parents'\Nfrom whom I was separated at the age of 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.26,Default,Mine Hisashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:497718,499261}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.26,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:499261,500262}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.84,Default,Mine Hisashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:500262,501847}Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:22.68,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:501847,502681}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.84,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:502681,503849}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.64,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:508229,509647}Hisashi, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.85,Default,Mine Hisashi,0,0,0,,{TIME:509647,511857}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:42.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:518364,522076}{\i1}I was their only son, but they had\Ndecided to give me up for adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.28,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:522076,525287}{\i1}They were so poor that\Ncouldn't even feed me properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.49,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:525287,526497}{\i1}I was pale and sickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:51.87,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:526497,531877}{\i1}Over time, I recovered, and when I started\Ngoing to school, I was already better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.46,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:532711,535464}{\i1}It was spring back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.63,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:535464,539635}{\i1}I had heard that my\Nreal parents had another daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:03.34,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:539635,543347}{\i1}Apparently\NI had a younger sister now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.65,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:558362,561657}{\i1}That younger sister…\Nwas Nozomi all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:24.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:561657,564910}{\i1}My first love\Nwas my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.28,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:564910,567288}{\i1}It's like some sick cosmic joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:567288,569290}{\i1}What did we do to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.63,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:574837,576630}Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:576630,578048}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:41.21,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:578048,581218}Hey, Fanni.\NTime's up. It is showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.42,Default,Boxer,0,0,0,,{TIME:581218,583429}Good luck and have courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.72,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:586015,587725}Here comes the champion\Nin the making!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.06,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:587725,590060}Pulverize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.93,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:591228,592938}– Good luck, Bro!\N– Good luck, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:57.56,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:593647,597568}{\i1}I feel like total crap\Nand you're telling me to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.15,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:597568,599153}{\i1}You're telling me to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:605868,608496}{\i1}Do not forget, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:608496,611415}{\i1}We'll cross the rainbow bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:17.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:611415,617087}{\i1}Beyond that bridge, there's\Na bright beautiful future waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.93,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:622551,625930}{\i1}It all went to hell.\NI can't cross that bridge anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.47,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:625930,627473}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.85,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:634271,636857}What the hell, Fanni?\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.66,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:648744,650663}What's wrong?\NYou're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.66,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:650663,652665}Where's your usual power?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.50,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:656460,658504}– Good luck, Bro!\N– Good luck, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.43,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:668305,671433}He's getting beaten!\NWhat do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.85,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:673352,674853}Come with me, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:27.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:686115,687741}This is Egawa's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.20,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:687741,690202}Sis, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:690202,692705}Oh, it's you, Kazuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:692705,694081}Sis is busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.12,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:694081,697126}Fanni is in trouble!\NHe's getting beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:697126,699253}Huh? Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:699253,701088}Thanks for letting me know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:702172,705259}I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:705259,707052}Go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:48.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:707052,708262}Huh? But—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.59,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:708262,709597}I'm telling you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:710389,712016}Y-Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:712016,713100}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.40,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:722860,724403}{\i1}She's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.15,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:725154,726155}{\i1}She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.11,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:726155,727114}{\i1}She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.19,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:727114,728198}{\i1}She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.03,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:728198,729033}{\i1}She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.57,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:729033,729575}{\i1}She's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.07,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:729575,731076}– She's…\N– Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.16,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:731827,733162}{\i1}My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:733162,735372}{\i1}Sister. Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:735372,736373}{\i1}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:736373,737374}{\i1}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.33,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:737374,738334}{\i1}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.75,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:738334,739752}{\i1}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:741837,743339}{\i1}Hang in there, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:27.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:743339,747301}{\i1}I'm coming. Clench your teeth\Nand hold on until I'm there.
