Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:769665,771792}{\i1}"A promising freshman\Nmysteriously disappears".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:776797,777715}{\i1}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:777715,779466}{\i1}Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:779466,783095}{\i1}I took a cab and went\Nto the hall to see you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:783095,785180}{\i1}Why didn't you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:786515,789184}{\i1}What am I going to do\Nnow that you left me all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:793105,795441}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:796817,799403}Do you expect me\Nto keep on singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:799403,800946}It's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,804700}Oh, that looks dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:804700,805826}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:807244,809038}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:29.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:809038,809830}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.20,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:812124,814209}By the way, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:814209,815377}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.21,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:816879,819214}I know what you're\Ngoing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.84,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:819214,821842}But you're not\Nthe only one who's hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.51,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:823052,826513}Fanni Moriyama, who has\Ndisappeared on you without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:826513,829975}I suspect that he might be hurting\Neven more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:53.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:829975,833354}But I don't understand\Nhim at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:59.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:834772,839401}The Fanni I know, if he had to lose,\Nhe would lose with dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:839401,842363}and wouldn't be so cowardly\Nto disappear just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844990,847368}So why did Fanni do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:848202,849161}Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.45,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:850120,852456}That he has chosen to disappear\Nwithout telling you anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:16.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:852456,856835}must have happened for a specific reason,\Nwhich we don't know. I cannot imagine otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.62,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:856835,858629}That is the only possible scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:859505,861131}Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:861131,864426}To love means to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:864426,866095}To believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.30,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:866095,869306}No matter what anyone says,\Nyou need to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:35.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:870682,875062}And until the day comes when\Nhe appears in front of you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:875062,877523}you should wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:877523,878982}Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:885197,886156}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:890536,892287}Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:892287,894164}Believe in Fanni and wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:895332,897668}Sir, I'll wait for him,\Nno matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:899878,901880}Ah, what lovely birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:06.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:903924,906552}That's the Mine I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:906552,909012}I'm going to sound boring,\Nbut what about our dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:909012,912224}Ah! I'm sorry.\NI'll finish it real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:912224,913684}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:916687,917938}Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:936248,937916}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.04,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:937916,940043}Mother, it's me, Hisashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.46,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:943172,944465}Hisashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.38,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:948260,949386}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.89,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:959229,960898}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.90,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:967196,969907}Excuse me,\Nwho might you be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.03,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:969907,971033}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.28,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:971033,972284}You don't recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.78,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:972284,973785}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:973785,974912}It's me, Hisashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.28,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:975579,977289}Hisashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:977289,978916}Still doesn't ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.12,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:978916,981126}Has my face changed so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.54,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:981126,983545}It's me, Hisashi, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:984880,986298}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.67,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:989968,991678}Ah! It's you, Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:991678,994806}Well, well, finally you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.84,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:994806,995849}Hisashi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.85,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:995849,997851}Watch your step, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.64,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:998936,1000646}It's been 17 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.52,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000646,1002523}I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.35,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002523,1005359}Why did you go to see me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:50.11,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005359,1010113}When I had heard the Moriyama-san couple have\Npassed away, I looked for you everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.86,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010113,1011865}Where have you been until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.20,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016703,1020207}It would be too long to explain,\Nbut let's say that I was in a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.25,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020207,1023252}Come in, darling.\NI want to know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023252,1024378}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:09.38,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025879,1029383}I have to board a ship in Yokohama\Nthat is leaving at 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.38,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030509,1031385}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.88,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032761,1033887}I'm going to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:15.88,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034930,1035889}America?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.05,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038100,1039059}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039059,1041311}Mother, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.48,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041311,1043480}Yes. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:26.06,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043480,1046066}Take a good look\Nat my face, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:29.94,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046066,1049945}I've decided to leave for America\Nto be able to realize my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.73,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050779,1052739}I want to succeed,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.95,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052739,1054950}But if, by chance,\NI'm not gonna make it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.20,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057619,1061206}I probably will not go back to Japan\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.04,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061206,1063041}Hisashi…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.25,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063041,1067254}So before leaving Japan I wanted to see\Nmy mother for the last time and thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.26,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070841,1073260}Mother, thank you\Nfor giving birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.92,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073760,1074928}Hisashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.01,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074928,1077014}You… You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.64,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078390,1079641}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.27,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079641,1083270}I'm sorry for giving you up\Nfor adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.77,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084479,1087774}Don't cry, Mother.\NThat's ancient history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.86,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087774,1089860}More importantly…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.36,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089860,1092362}You look rather pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.90,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092362,1093905}Huh? N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.28,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093905,1096283}I feel well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.54,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100662,1103540}It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.79,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103540,1107794}If you say so. But you need to take good care\Nof yourself and you must live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.75,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107794,1109755}Yes, yes. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109755,1111298}Alright then.\NI'm going, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.46,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113925,1115469}I'll work hard in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115469,1116803}Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.64,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116803,1119640}Ah, tell Father\NI dropped by and said "hi".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.35,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122142,1123352}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.81,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124519,1126813}Hisashi, let me see you\None last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.98,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128732,1129983}Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131443,1132319}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.74,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138158,1139743}{\i1}Hisashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:03.78,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139743,1143789}{\i1}Your mother might become\Nblind very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.54,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143789,1146541}{\i1}But I won't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.87,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146541,1149878}{\i1}You're leaving for America now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.83,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149878,1151838}{\i1}I don't want you\Nto worry, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:17.01,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151838,1157010}{\i1}I will wait for the day when you\Nreturn having accomplished your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169773,1172150}This is Egawa's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172150,1175654}Oh, Mom?\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175654,1177781}Huh? My older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:43.28,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178365,1183286}Yes. I'd like you to go\Nto Yokohama and see him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184454,1185997}Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:48.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185997,1188291}Hisashi is going to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190669,1192713}I understand.\NI'm going right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:04.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198260,1204808}The passenger ship Miranda\Nto San Francisco departs soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.68,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204808,1207686}Please step away from the ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208395,1209688}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209688,1210856}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210856,1213900}Excuse me.\NPlease let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214526,1216153}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218697,1220907}Hisashi! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220907,1223326}It's me, Mine Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224911,1227914}Hisashi, it's your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227914,1229916}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230333,1231960}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233670,1235422}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236173,1238425}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239593,1241178}It's me, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243513,1245432}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246099,1248602}I'm here to see you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:54.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253356,1254649}Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254649,1256401}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256401,1258111}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258111,1259571}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.49,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261406,1262491}Nozomi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.11,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263950,1266119}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266119,1269039}Fanni! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269039,1271708}Why are you leaving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271708,1274628}I don't want you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274628,1276630}Come back to me, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278799,1280550}Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.88,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282928,1284888}{\i1}Nozomi, forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284888,1286807}{\i1}You're better off\Nif you forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286807,1288892}Come back, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288892,1291228}Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291228,1293396}I'm begging you, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293396,1296233}Where are you going, Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.44,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297901,1299444}{\i1}There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.44,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299444,1301446}{\i1}We're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.40,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302113,1304407}{\i1}Farewell, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:58.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314251,1318630}"There's nothing good about\Na canary that forgot its song.{NOTE:歌を忘れたカナリヤに魅力はない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:01.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318630,1321049}Work hard and become\Na great singer."{NOTE:栄光に向かって羽ばたけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:10.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329224,1330475}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:18.77,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332477,1338775}{\i1}Nozomi went to see Fanni off,\Nbut she saw only her lover in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:24.32,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338775,1344322}{\i1}What she didn't know is that Fanni\Nwas actually her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:38.46,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355667,1358461}Good luck, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.83,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358461,1360839}Stay safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384487,1385697}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385697,1387407}{\i1}I will wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:08.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387407,1388658}{\i1}I will wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388658,1391202}{\i1}Until you return to me.\NNo matter how long it takes.
Comment: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:25.43,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1405433,1405433}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:32.63,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407627,1412632}{\i1}Fanni leaves Nozomi alone and\Ngoes on a journey across the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.05,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412632,1415051}{\i1}On top of having to deal\Nwith her broken heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415051,1419389}{\i1}Nozomi gets an invoice for 200,000 yen\Nfor her father's medical care.
