Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:48.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424519,1428898}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"A Journey Towards Tomorrow".{NOTE:明日への旅立ち}
